~/.config/polybar/themes:

⭕ 〢POLYBAR THEME FILE CHEAT SHEET: 
        ( Add your own as you wish!)

            ・ theme - theme icon ( paintbrush icon located on bottom bar )
            ・ ttbar - top toolbar on right ( bluetooth, network, brightness, and battery icons )
            ・ circle - rofi app launcher button ( circle icon on bottom left )
            ・ msc - music buttons ( back, play, and forward icons on bottom right )
            ・ star - eww sidebar launcher button ( star icon located on top left )
            ・ updates - number of updates ( located to the right of pacman icon, bottom center )
            ・ title = music title ( music title / 'no music playing' on bottom right )
            ・ pacman - pacman icon ( pacman icon on bottom bar in the center, next to time )
